<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Weird" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Weird</orth> (O. Edd. <emph>weyard</emph> or <emph>weyward;</emph> later Ff in <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 136</bibl> <emph>wizard.</emph> Monosyll. in <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 2</bibl>; dissyll. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 20</bibl> and <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 136</bibl>; dubious in <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 32</bibl> &amp; <bibl n="shak. mac 3.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 133</bibl>) subservient to Destiny: <cit><quote>the w. sisters,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 32</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.4.133" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 136</bibl>. <cit><quote>w. women,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 3.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 2</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>